Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Come on, stud.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.22,0:00:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got it all set up for you to go out\Nwith our niece.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, come on out here and meet Peter\NGriffin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Peter, this is our niece, Jennifer Love\NHewitt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0031D1FD&}Nice to meet you{\c&H00FFFFFF&}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm getting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. Peter Griffin. So, Where do you want\Nto go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go Anywhere except the disco. They\Ndon't let me in there anymore.
